Ok so last night i was soo emotional.. As a matter of fact I have been that way for a while now which is weird for me.. Eric and I got into a fight today and actually sat down to talk it all out.. It worked out for the best for us to talk about it cuz what always happends is i bottle up what is bothering me and then just blow up on him in the end.. So we talked and there is going to be a lot of changes in our relationship.. One of the biggest ones is we are going to talk. 

It really sucks to not have friends and be all alone all the time.. It hurts when i have to sit at home and do nothing if eric is going out with the guys and stuff.. I feel like im makin him feel bad for me by getting upset that he wants to hang out with his friends which is not fair to him.. He should be able to have friends and a girlfriend and i understand that.. I just with i had my old life back.. I just want to be able to have fun just sitting around with the friends like the good old days instead of working my ass off just to be able to have like an hour of fun that i have to pay for.. Its really hard to be older and im being to regret ever wanting to be older.. I mean im stuck.. Im only 18 which means i can buy my own ciggarettes and i can get lotto tickets and rent porn but i still cant go to bar with my bf or n e thing that older people do.. So for so long i wanted to be 18 and be able to do whatever i want but its not much different then being 17 cuz i still cant drink and have fun like the people older than me do.. Its just like being stuck in limbo.. I dont want to hang out with the people who are younger cuz they ask if i can buy ciggs for them but the people older i have to ask to buy beer for me lmao.. SOO STUPID! 

All i really want is my old life back were i had a million people to call to hang out and i never had a dull moment.. 

Man it felt good to get all that out! lol...

Im going to a concert on the 11th!!! Less than jake!!! Im so excited but i hurt my back so i cant stand in the front which really sucks.. We'll see tho!! 

Ok well im gonna go for now! Thanks for reading!!

**~~N!kk!~~**

I have been up way too long.. Im so tired but i have so much on my mind not even my meds can help me sleep tonight.. Its 5am and im thinking about bills, moving, the whole boyfriend situation.. (my bf is driving me NUTS!) and sooo much more...

It all started about 3 weeks ago.. I started having a strange pain in my back.. Well 2 weeks later the pain had gotten so bad that i couldnt even get up from my bed.. Mom rushed me to the hospital at 4am and they said i sprained my back.. Im now on two pain killers and a muscual relaxer.. The pain isnt n e better when im not on my meds either.. so i dont know what the fuck im gonna do when i run out...

Then... 

My dad called me 3 nights ago about 8pm.. I was at work. He was in the back of a cop car on his way to spend the next 3 months in jail for being the fucktard he is... I was standing in the fitting rooms at work trying not to get caught by a manager for talkin on my phone.. It was kinda hard considering i was crying.. Ok i take that back more like sobbing... I had to take a break to have a ciggarette and think about the shit that had just been dropped on me.. Its so hard to think about how things are now when they were so perfect 3 years ago..

The whole bf situation is so messed up i dont know what to do about it.. I love my bf with all my heart dont get me wrong its just i want to be treated better.. Is that so much to ask? I want to know he wants me and i dont feel like he does half the time.. Plus im getting all worked up about his ex gf situation.. That bitch drives me fucking insane. Whenever her name is even said i get all weird.. This has never happened to me before but then again i have never dated a guy who still has his ex on his phone plan and constantly lets her fuck him over... I dont know.. She thinks its none of my business but what happeneds to my bf and his money i believe is my business.. Exspecially when we cant go out cuz he doesnt have money due to her pure stupidity... Man that women is fucking stupid..

So n e ways.. I have been working a lot which is good cuz i sure as hell need the money... Too many bills and not enough money coming in to get them all paid... Who woulda thought that when i tured 18 i would have so many bills already?! NOT ME!!! Oh well its life and im getting back handed full force by reality.. 

Thats all for now.. Thanks for reading!

**~~N!kk!~~**

So it has been a while since i wrote in here again.. It seems like time has been working against me latley.. Its like once I get a day off to just relax its over in an instant and im working again. So for thanksgiving I went to PA to visit Jons sister Chrissy and her fiance Ron.. I had a great time.. I wish we could have stayed longer so we didnt have to sit in the car again! Naw but it was a kool trip.. To be honest with u PA is a lot different than Illinois... I liked it tho.. Yeah so we got a hotel room that had a indoor pool so everyone was up at 9am to go swimming but i took a shower instead lol.. I felt bad tho cuz we didnt get to eat at rons grandparents house after his poor grandmother slaved over the stove to make us all a night dinner. I thought it was kool getting to hang out with Chrissy tho cuz i talked to her on the phone a lot and it was my first time to actually meet her. At first I was REALLY nervous but the second i walked in the door I kinda felt like I was visiting an old friend  Well then i came back here to the sucky town i live in and got a second job  its kinda hard sometimes cuz if im not working one job im working the other and i dont get a break for the next 12 days... Once again i had to work a double at Adventure trails and I got writen up for not taking my garbage around. I honestly forgot cuz im not used to having to do that im used to the outside guys coming and stealing it.. But i have to keep myself going. I want a car and right about now i will do almost anything to get it. Like spend all my money on christmas!!! HAHAHA! Oh well after christmas it should be easier to save.. SO I THINK... But im also paying for my birthday party!!!! Im paying for it cuz i want a nice 18th birthday and my mother cant afford it so I am leaving it up to myself!!! So I hope everyone who goes has a great time!!!! So yeah its getting late I think maybe I should rap this up for now.. I will try to keep blogs going!!! 

goodnight!!! ** Nikki **
